statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_type, outcome_result, measurement_value FROM quantum_experiments
SELECT experiment_date, experiment_type FROM quantum_experiments WHERE outcome_result = 'Success'
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments WHERE experiment_date > '2021-01-01'
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_type FROM quantum_experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments WHERE experiment_type = 'Bell Test';
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, outcome_result FROM quantum_experiments WHERE measurement_value > 0.5 ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT experiment_type, COUNT(*) AS num_experiments FROM quantum_experiments GROUP BY experiment_type HAVING num_experiments > 3;
SELECT DISTINCT experiment_date FROM quantum_experiments WHERE outcome_result = 'Success' ORDER BY experiment_date ASC;
SELECT AVG(measurement_value) AS avg_measurement_value, MAX(measurement_value) AS max_measurement_value FROM quantum_experiments WHERE experiment_type = 'Entanglement Test';
SELECT * FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements;
SELECT measurement_id, experiment_name FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements ORDER BY measurement_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements WHERE experiment_name='Quantum teleportation';
SELECT * FROM ExperimentParticipants JOIN QuantumExperimentMeasurements ON ExperimentParticipants.experiment_id = QuantumExperimentMeasurements.measurement_id;

SELECT participant_id, participant_name, experiment_name FROM ExperimentParticipants JOIN QuantumExperimentMeasurements ON ExperimentParticipants.experiment_id = QuantumExperimentMeasurements.measurement_id ORDER BY participant_name ASC;
SELECT measurement_id, experiment_name, measurement_outcome FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements;
SELECT * FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements WHERE measurement_date > '2021-10-01';
SELECT experiment_name, COUNT(*) AS total_measurements FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements GROUP BY experiment_name;
SELECT e.experiment_name, p.participant_name FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements e INNER JOIN ExperimentParticipants p ON e.measurement_id = p.experiment_id;
SELECT DISTINCT measurement_outcome FROM QuantumExperimentMeasurements ORDER BY measurement_outcome DESC;
SELECT * FROM Experiment;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM Experiment WHERE researcher_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT id, measurement_value FROM Measurement WHERE id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT analysis_result FROM Analysis ORDER BY analysis_result DESC;
SELECT * FROM Experiment WHERE experiment_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY experiment_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Experiment;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date, researcher_name FROM Experiment WHERE experiment_date > '2022-01-01';

SELECT Experiment.experiment_name, Measurement.measurement_value, Analysis.analysis_result FROM (Experiment JOIN Measurement ON Experiment.id = Measurement.experiment_id) JOIN Analysis ON Measurement.id = Analysis.measurement_id WHERE Measurement.measurement_value > 50;

SELECT Experiment.experiment_name, COUNT(Analysis.id) AS analysis_count FROM Experiment LEFT JOIN Measurement ON Experiment.id = Measurement.experiment_id LEFT JOIN Analysis ON Measurement.id = Analysis.measurement_id GROUP BY Experiment.id;

SELECT researcher_name, AVG(measurement_value) AS avg_measurement_value FROM Experiment JOIN Measurement ON Experiment.id = Measurement.experiment_id GROUP BY researcher_name HAVING AVG(measurement_value) > 25;
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, measurement_outcome FROM quantum_experiments WHERE measurement_outcome = 'success';
SELECT experiment_name, quantum_system FROM quantum_experiments ORDER BY experiment_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiment_results WHERE measurement_result > 0.5;
SELECT system_name, qubits FROM quantum_systems WHERE qubits >= 2;
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, quantum_system FROM quantum_experiments WHERE measurement_outcome = 'success';
SELECT experiment_name, measurement_time FROM quantum_experiments JOIN experiment_results ON quantum_experiments.experiment_id = experiment_results.experiment_id WHERE measurement_result > 0.5;
SELECT system_name, qubits FROM quantum_systems ORDER BY qubits DESC;
SELECT device_name, manufacturer, quantum_compatible FROM measurement_devices WHERE quantum_compatible = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM quantum_experiments WHERE id = 1 ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM experimental_conditions WHERE temperature > 300 ORDER BY pressure ASC;
SELECT experiment_id, measurement_time, measurement_result FROM measurement_data ORDER BY measurement_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT name, email, affiliation FROM experimentalists WHERE experience_years >= 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiments WHERE outcome = 'Success' ORDER BY start_time DESC, experiment_name ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM quantum_experiments WHERE outcome = 'Failure' AND start_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY start_time ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT e.experiment_name, ec.temperature, ec.pressure, ec.humidity FROM quantum_experiments e JOIN experimental_conditions ec ON e.id = ec.experiment_id WHERE ec.temperature > 25 AND ec.pressure < 100 ORDER BY ec.temperature DESC, ec.pressure ASC LIMIT 20

SELECT m.measurement_time, m.measurement_result, m.measurement_error, e.name AS experimenter_name FROM measurement_data m JOIN experimentalists e ON m.experiment_id = e.experimenter_id WHERE e.experience_years > 5 ORDER BY m.measurement_time ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT eq.equipment_id, eq.equipment_name, eq.manufacturer, eq.purchase_date, eq.warranty_period FROM equipment eq WHERE eq.purchase_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY eq.equipment_name ASC LIMIT 3
